---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';
import Quote from '../components/Quote.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Kevin 'The General' Neal" description="The story behind the stage name. Kevin Neal is a 2× CCMA-nominated pedal steel player based in Hamilton, Ontario.">
  <Nav />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section-label">// About</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">The Story Behind<br><span>The General</span></h1>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lede">His stage name wasn't chosen. It was earned.</p>

        <p>A university-trained musician with an instinct for the spaces between notes, Kevin "The General" Neal has built one of the most respected reputations in Canadian country music &mdash; not through self-promotion, but through the undeniable authority of his playing.</p>

        <p>Based in Hamilton, Ontario, Kevin's career spans decades of live performance, studio sessions, and collaborative work with artists at every level. His primary instrument is the pedal steel guitar, though he is equally accomplished on dobro.</p>

        <h2>On Stage</h2>
        <p>Kevin has shared stages with some of the biggest names in North American country, performing at landmark venues and festivals including the <strong>Calgary Stampede</strong>, <strong>Mariposa Folk Festival</strong>, and other major festival stages around the world.</p>

        <h2>In the Studio & On the Road</h2>
        <p>Kevin has recorded with artists across multiple genres and continents. His longstanding work with <strong>Jade Eagleson</strong> &mdash; from the studio recording of <em>Steal My Girl</em> to Eagleson's 2025&ndash;2026 <strong>Coming Soon to a Honky Tonk Near You</strong> headlining tour across Canada and the U.S. &mdash; reflects the trust that top-tier artists place in his playing. His session and touring work spans CMA Fest, CCMA Awards stages, the Calgary Stampede, K-Days, Cavendish Beach, and beyond.</p>

        <h2>Recognition</h2>
        <p>Twice nominated for <strong>CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year</strong>, Kevin's credentials come from the people who know the instrument best &mdash; fellow musicians and industry peers who recognize the rare combination of technical mastery and musical intelligence he brings to every room.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-portrait">
          <img src="/kevin4.png" alt="Kevin Neal" />
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>2&times; CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year nominee</li>
            <li>Grand Ole Opry performance credit</li>
            <li>3 continents, countless stages</li>
            <li>University-trained, multi-instrumentalist</li>
            <li>Based in Hamilton, ON</li>
            <li>Available worldwide</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3>Instruments</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Pedal Steel (primary)</li>
            <li>Dobro / Resonator</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <Quote
    text="His approach is systematic, tactical, and unfailingly musical. He reads a room, serves the song, and elevates the artist."
    attribution="On The General's approach"
  />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 160px 60px 60px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .page-title span {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 60px 60px 100px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .about-text .lede {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .about-text p + p { margin-top: 24px; }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-text :global(strong) {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .sidebar-portrait {
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .sidebar-portrait img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .sidebar-block {
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.02);
  }

  .sidebar-block h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .sidebar-block ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .sidebar-block li {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--light-mid);
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.08);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .sidebar-block li::before {
    content: '— ';
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .sidebar-block li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 120px 32px 40px; }
    .about-content { padding: 40px 32px 60px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .about-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
